name: droning loop 001: guidance (EADGBE)
description: Recorded and created by Gustavo Paim. Follow me on tt and ig: @colapsismo.   For buyers, since H=N only allows 40MB, I can send you the original files. Contact me: gustavo.h.paim@gmail.com. This is the first of a series of droning loops i've been making. The sound aims to guide you to a meditative state of abstraction of sameness and perception of difference. At the end, the listener will notice that no parts of the piece sound the same.
